reviewText:
Everyone NEEDS to hear this!

This is what people really need to hear. I love the way Dale doesn't hold any punches and tells it like it is. Out of all of the books, seminars, trainings, videos THIS is one of my top all time favorites. If you haven't connected with Dale... you need to. Thank you Dale!

Dale Calvert delivers. You might not like what you hear, but this video is right on target. Great inspiration for anyone. Whether you need motivation for your business, or just need a kick start in general.
